    {
      "chinese": "以前阿美族人生活非常不容易，種玉米、稻田沒有發展，連地瓜都吃不到，小孩唸書繳不起學費，為了家庭生計，就只好到台北的礦坑工作。",
      "ab": "Itiya ho ko ’Amis a tamdaw, cowa kanga’ay ko ’orip, paloma to ariray, panay, awaay ko kacomahadan, o konga’ to awaay a makaen, o payci to awaay ko sapateli to sapitakeci no kaemangay. Sakanga’ayaw no ’orip, tayra sanay to i Taypak a misikitang.",
